<% provide(:email_title, 'Account Password Change Successful') %>

<p>This is to notify that the password for your account has been changed.</p>

<p>If you did not request this password change, please immediately go to the following link and reset your password:</p>

<%= link_to "Reset your Password", new_password_reset_url %>

<p>If the link above does not work, copy and paste the following url into your browser:</p>

<%= new_password_reset_url %>

<p>You should also verify that other accounts which may use the same email address and/or password have not been compromised.</p>

<p>Please contact us directly if you require any assistance.</p>
